data.description: This 1448 sq ft home sits on 28.62 acres located in the Paradise Ranchos area of Winnemucca, NV. Featuring new flooring and freshly updated kitchen and bathrooms. With plenty of space for all your outdoor activities and animals with gorgeous mountain views. Come enjoy the luxuries of country living with this great opportunity. Property is fenced and cross fenced.
